item.title: Photography on manual: 7 –; Small Cat
item.description: My parents’ cat, called Milly. Who I call “Small Cat” because she’s so small. **Small Cat.** I edited out the wonky lamp in the background because it was distracting. I also muted the grass and plants so her scary green eyes would be more noticeable.
